flowchart TD
    A([Start]) --> B[User opens Book List]
    B --> C[System loads first page 10 books]
    C --> D{Action?}
    D -->|Search by name/author| E[Apply keyword search] --> C
    D -->|Filter by category| F[Apply category filter] --> C
    D -->|Sort| G[Sort by Name A-Z / Year desc / Popularity] --> C
    D -->|Pagination| H[Go to selected page] --> C
    D -->|View detail| I[Open selected book detail]
    I --> Z([End])
